1.	MongoDB Basics

 (a)Write a MongoDB query to create and drop database
> use school
>db.students.insertMany([{name:"Aarchie",age:20,rollno:22},{name:"Tanvi",age:21,rollno:07},{name:"Ravi",age:18,rollno:33},{name:"Vikrant",age:22,rollno:06}])
>db.dropDatabase()
 

(b) Write a MongoDB query to create, display and drop collection
>use school
>db.students.insertMany([{name:"Aarchie",age:20,rollno:22},{name:"Tanvi",age:21,rollno:07},{name:"Ravi",age:18,rollno:33},{name:"Vikrant",age:22,rollno:06}])
>db.students.find()
>db.students.drop()
 

